name: Nike N7
description:
This is a lined drawstring backpack/gym bag made by Nike. 
 The bag is navy blue in color and features a silvery diamond pattern, an outside zipper pocket, decorative black mesh, double rope drawstring/backpack straps, the Nike swoosh and the text You're an athlete. Train like one.
 The bag measures about 18.5 tall and 12.5 wide.
 It is in great pre-owned condition with the original tags still attached.
